445
00:28:34.480 --> 00:28:37.760
- Tell him what?
- That I'm always right.

446
00:28:39.920 --> 00:28:41.680
Say it.

447
00:28:41.680 --> 00:28:45.400
- The cats are relevant. and you
are always right. my amazing wife.

448
00:28:47.960 --> 00:28:50.800
- Come on.
It's never hard for me to say that.

449
00:28:50.800 --> 00:28:53.480
D-d-d-d-d-d― Wait.
- Mm-mm. Oh no. no. no.

450
00:28:53.480 --> 00:28:56.240
No. no. no. no.
- Yes. yes. yes. yes. yes. yes.
- Later. later. later. later.

451
00:28:56.240 --> 00:28:58.920
We need to look at Poppy.
- Poppy.

452
00:29:00.560 --> 00:29:02.840
Later. I'm holding you to that.

453
00:29:02.840 --> 00:29:05.840
Never hard for you to do that either.

454
00:29:16.600 --> 00:29:19.440
Nice place.
- Just a quick visit. right?

455
00:29:19.440 --> 00:29:22.360
I really wanna get back to
... later.

456
00:29:22.360 --> 00:29:26.440
- We will get back
to later. I promise.

457
00:29:26.720 --> 00:29:30.320
So Poppy is a part-time chef
at a vegan cafe.

458
00:29:31.520 --> 00:29:35.000
Youngest member of
the Mowai Bay Council.

459
00:29:35.200 --> 00:29:37.200
Ah. Look at that.

460
00:29:37.520 --> 00:29:42.720
She gate-crashed a fashion show
and threw fake blood on someone
wearing a fur coat.

461
00:29:42.720 --> 00:29:44.920
