to save the birds.

463
00:29:50.680 --> 00:29:52.680
- Oh.

464
00:30:08.800 --> 00:30:10.800
- Backpack.

465
00:30:12.480 --> 00:30:14.480
- Wait. Is that...

466
00:30:14.880 --> 00:30:16.880
moving?

467
00:30:17.800 --> 00:30:20.160
