about to go for a swim.

468
00:30:20.160 --> 00:30:22.120
Hey!

469
00:30:22.120 --> 00:30:24.120
- Poppy!

470
00:30:24.160 --> 00:30:26.160
Poppy. stop!

471
00:30:27.520 --> 00:30:29.360
