Gonna go for a paddle and a picnic.

473
00:30:35.520 --> 00:30:38.720
- Wine that miaows.
- OK. I have to say it.

474
00:30:38.720 --> 00:30:42.520
Let the cat out of the bag. Poppy.

475
00:30:49.920 --> 00:30:53.880
- I didn't hurt any of them.
- So how many cats have you taken?

476
00:30:53.880 --> 00:30:57.160
