- And put them on Barren Island.

477
00:30:57.160 --> 00:31:00.920
- I'm protecting
our Mowai Bay birds.
- There's nothing on Barren Island.

478
00:31:00.920 --> 00:31:04.640
There's nothing for them to eat.
-  recognise that.

479
00:31:04.640 --> 00:31:10.320
Look ― I tried to cull the cats. but
 couldn't bring myself to.

480
00:31:10.400 --> 00:31:13.440
So I kayak over every night
to feed them.

481
00:31:13.440 --> 00:31:15.320
They're all fine. They...

482
00:31:15.320 --> 00:31:17.520
kinda became a cat family.

483
00:31:17.720 --> 00:31:22.840
- OK. so on Friday night. you went
to Gordon's with the intention
of just taking his cat.

484
00:31:22.840 --> 00:31:25.480
